XTANDI

IS BEING DEVELOPED AND COMMERCIALIZED IN COLLABORATION WITH ASTELLAS. THE TWO COMPANIES SHARE EQUALLY IN THE GROSS PROFITS (LOSSES) RELATED TO U.S. NET SALES OF

XTANDI

. SUBJECT TO CERTAIN EXCEPTIONS, PFIZER AND ASTELLAS ALSO SHARE EQUALLY ALL XTANDI COMMERCIALIZATION COSTS ATTRIBUTABLE TO THE U.S. MARKET. PFIZER AND ASTELLAS ALSO SHARE CERTAIN DEVELOPMENT AND OTHER COLLABORATION EXPENSES AND PFIZER RECEIVES TIERED ROYALTIES AS A PERCENTAGE OF INTERNATIONAL

XTANDI

