ITEM 2.

PROPERTIES

IN 2016, WE CONTINUED TO CONSOLIDATE OPERATIONS TO ACHIEVE EFFICIENCIES AND DISPOSE OF EXCESS SPACE. AS OF DECEMBER 31, 2016, WE HAD 567 OWNED AND LEASED PROPERTIES, AMOUNTING TO APPROXIMATELY 57 MILLION SQUARE FEET.

IN 2016, WE REDUCED THE NUMBER OF PROPERTIES IN OUR PORTFOLIO BY 28 SITES AND 2.3 MILLION SQUARE FEET WITH THE DISPOSAL OF SURPLUS REAL PROPERTY ASSETS AND WITH REDUCTIONS OF OPERATING SPACE IN ALL REGIONS. THESE REDUCTIONS INCLUDE PARTIAL OFFSETS DUE TO ACQUISITIONS OF ANACOR, BAMBOO THERAPEUTICS INC., SUBSTANTIALLY ALL OF THE ASSETS OF BIND THERAPEUTICS, INC. AND MEDIVATION.

PFIZER CONTINUES TO OWN AND LEASE SPACE AROUND THE WORLD FOR SALES AND MARKETING, CUSTOMER SERVICE, REGULATORY COMPLIANCE, R&D, MANUFACTURING AND DISTRIBUTION, AND ADMINISTRATIVE SUPPORT FUNCTIONS. IN MANY LOCATIONS, BUSINESS LINES AND OPERATIONS ARE CO-LOCATED TO ACHIEVE SYNERGY AND OPERATIONAL EFFICIENCIES.

