FORM 10-K SUMMARY

A FORM 10-K SUMMARY IS PROVIDED AT THE BEGINNING OF THIS 2016 FORM 10-K, WITH HYPERLINKED CROSS-REFERENCES. THIS ALLOWS USERS TO EASILY LOCATE THE CORRESPONDING ITEMS IN THIS 2016 FORM 10-K, WHERE THE DISCLOSURE IS FULLY PRESENTED. THE SUMMARY DOES NOT INCLUDE CERTAIN PART III INFORMATION THAT IS INCORPORATED BY REFERENCE FROM OUR 2017 PROXY STATEMENT.

